title.rendered: Fiji Rattan Round Set Glass Dining – various sizes

content.rendered:
The Fiji Rattan Round Glass Dining Set is a luxurious item, ideal for pub gardens, restaurant patios & other busy commercial venues with outdoor spaces. The Fiji is hardwearing and durable, ready for every day use.

The Fiji is made with 5mm industrial round PE rattan to ensure the Fiji is comfortable and classically designed. The frames are made from welded aluminium which is then powder coated to give extra protection against corrosion. 

The weighty table top is thick 12mm tempered glass which gives extra strength and stability. Perfect for alfresco dining and a 40mm diameter parasol hole will accommodate a parasol should you need one. The chairs come fully assembled with matching dark grey cushions.

Some items may require basic self assembly. Table accessories (plants etc.) not included.


Dimensions in mm:

Table

  • H 750
  • Weight: 28kg (1000dia)
  • Weight: 55kg (1500mm dia)

Chairs

  • H 850 x D 750 x W 630
  • Weight: 10kg.
